EntityAvailabilityStatus EntityAvailabilityStatus Enum

In this Article

Edit

Enumerates the status of the entity availability.

Syntax

Declaration

[DataContract(Name = "EntityAvailabilityStatus", Namespace = "http://schemas.microsoft.com/netservices/2010/10/servicebus/connect")]
public enum EntityAvailabilityStatus<DataContract(Name:="EntityAvailabilityStatus", Namespace:="http://schemas.microsoft.com/netservices/2010/10/servicebus/connect")>
Public Enum EntityAvailabilityStatus

Fields

Available
Available

The entity is available.

Limited

The entity is limited.
Renaming
Renaming

The entity is being renamed.
Restoring
Restoring

The entity is being restored.
Unknown
Unknown

The entity is unknown.
